de%20to%20being%20the%20sole%20head%20of%20the%20household%2C%20though.%20While%20making%20sure%20we%20had%20everything%20we%20needed%20on%20my%20teaching%20salary%20was%20tough%2C%20I%20experienced%20an%20enormous%20sense%20of%20pride%20from%20working%20hard%20and%20finding%20ways%20to%20stretch%20our%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20always%20had%20the%20final%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20being%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-single-mother-reached-financial-independence-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esole%20provider%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20came%20being%20the%20sole%20decision-maker.%20While%20I%20always%20kept%20my%20son%20in%20mind%2C%20ultimately%2C%20I%20was%20the%20one%20who%20made%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20things%20like%20our%20home's%20decor%2C%20what%20was%20for%20dinner%2C%20and%20how%20we%20spent%20our%20free%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20consulting%20another%20adult%2C%20I%20only%20had%20to%20ask%20my%20son%20if%20spaghetti%20sounded%20good%20for%20dinner%2C%20or%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20the%20beach%20this%20weekend.%20While%20we%20sometimes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-bittersweet-changing-dynamic-with-daughter-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20our%20disagreements%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20choice%20was%20always%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20son%20and%20I%20formed%20a%20tight%20bond%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20just%20my%20son%20and%20me%2C%20everything%20that%20we%20did%20together%20became%20our%20thing.%20We%20formed%20countless%20inside%20jokes%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20communicate%20through%20facial%20expressions%20alone.%20We%20developed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-nesting-divorce-parenting-plan-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eday-to-day%20rituals%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20dance%20breaks%20after%20dinner%20an