t-tax-advantaged-accounts-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20left%20my%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20earning%20a%20salary%20again%2C%20so%20I%20can%20work%20on%20whatever%20I'm%20most%20passionate%20about.%20I%20spend%20my%20time%20building%20my%20startup%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thirdear.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThirdEar%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20AI%20that%20gives%20real-time%20help%20and%20suggestions%20without%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20ways%20I%20was%20able%20to%20do%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%C2%A0Avoid%20educational%20debt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Kerala%2C%20India%2C%20where%20my%20parents%20made%20less%20than%20%2420%2C000%20a%20year.%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20an%20undergraduate%20education%20in%20the%20US%20or%20even%20go%20to%20private%20colleges%20in%20India%20without%20taking%20on%20debt.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20study%20in%20a%20government%20college%20in%20India%20which%20is%20much%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20hard%20for%20a%20test%20students%20in%20India%20take%20every%20year%20for%20college%20admissions.%20I%20was%20ranked%20among%20the%20top%200.1%25%20and%20got%20to%20study%20engineering%20and%20physics%20at%20the%20India%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Bombay%2C%20a%20top%20public%20university%20in%20India.%20The%20entire%20cost%20was%20only%20about%20%241%2C200%20a%20year%2C%20including%20tuition%2C%20housing%2C%20and%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20taking%20on%20debt%20to%20pursue%20a%20master's%20degree%2C%20I%20applied%20directly%20for%20a%20Ph.D.%20program%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20in%20Urbana-Champaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20apply%20directly%20for%20Ph.D.%20programs%20in%20the%20US%20without%20getting%20a%20master's%20degree%20first.%20Ph.D.%20students%20at%20US%20universities%20will%20often%20get%20their%20tuition%20fees%20waived%20and%20rece