nakw.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20these%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2011%20towers%20with%206%2C000%20homes%20being%20built%20by%20the%20Squamish%20Nation%20on%20a%2012-acre%20piece%20of%20land%20near%20downtown%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada's%20most%20expensive%20real-estate%20market.%20The%20Squamish%20people%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fbritish-columbia%2Flittle-known-history-of-squamish-nation-land-in-vancouver-1.5104584%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforced%20off%20of%20this%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%2020th%20century%20and%20finally%20won%20back%20their%20ancestral%20territory%20about%2020%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20development%2C%20named%20Sen%CC%93a%CC%81k%CC%B1w%2C%20is%20on%20Squamish%20Nation%20reserve%20land%2C%20it's%20not%20subject%20to%20the%20same%20governmental%20land-use%20regulations%20as%20land%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20city%2C%20allowing%20for%20a%20speedier%20approval%20and%20construction%20process.%20The%20first%20three%20towers%20are%20set%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20November%202025%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20development%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20done%20in%20about%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMindy%20Wight%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Squamish%20development%20group%20building%20Sen%CC%93%C3%A1%E1%B8%B5w%2C%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bthe%20creation%20of%20a%20modern%20Squamish%20village%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWight%20sees%20Sen%CC%93a%CC%81k%CC%B1w%20and%20other%20indigenous%20developments%20as%20particularly%20innovative%20ways%20to%20solve%20the%20region's%20housing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20Nation%20benefits%20from%20generating%20wealth%20and%20prosperity%20for%20its%20members%2C%20it's%20actually%20solving%20some%20of%20those%20challenges%20that%20are%20facing%20Vancouver%2C%26quot%3B%20Wight%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20noted%20that%20about%2020%25%20of%20the%20units%20will%20be%20designated%20as%20affordable%20housing%2C%20and%20250%20units%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20Nation%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20housing%20is%20much%20needed%20for%20Vancouverites%2C%20especially%20First%20Nation%20members.%20Canada's%20federal%20auditor%20general%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnationalpost.com%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fauditor-general-slams-governments-failure-first-nations-housing%3Ftaid%3D65f9e43d90ad1e000175d3a5%26utm_campaign%3Dtrueanthem%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econdemned%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%26quot%3Bdistressing%20and%20persistent%20pattern%20of%20failure%26quot%3B%20by%20federal%20programs%20designed%20to%20support%20First%20Nations%20housing%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20among%20other%20services.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20discouraged%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20number%20of%20First%20Nations%20families%20forced%20to%20live%20in%20unsafe%20or%20inadequate%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22971%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20site%20of%20the%20Sen%CC%93%C3%A1%E1%B8%B5w%20development%20under%20construction%20in%20late%20February%202024%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66007c9f1caec1275a68d2e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22727%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConstruction%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Sen%CC%93%C3%A1%E1%B8%B5w%20development%20in%20late%20February%202024%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nch'%E1%B8%B5ay%CC%93%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20effort%2C%20three%20First%20Nations%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20Musqueam%2C%20Squamish%2C%20and%20Tsleil-Waututh%20peoples%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0came%20together%20to%20create%20a%20partnership%20to%20develop%20six%20different%20pieces%20of%20land%20in%20Vancouver%20and%20the%20surrounding%20area.%20The%20value%20of%20the%20land%20alone%2C%20which%20has%20been%20acquired%20by%20the%20Nations%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20now%20exceeds%20%244%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Brennan%20Cook%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20MST%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20company%20representing%20the%20three%20First%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20they're%20doing%20here%20is%20groundbreaking%2C%20it%20really%20hasn't%20been%20done%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20two%20major%20projects%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20the%20MST%20Development%20Corporation%20joined%20with%20the%20Canadian%20federal%20government%20to%20buy%20two%20large%20pieces%20of%20land%C2%A0in%20the%20city%20that%20will%20be%20developed%20into%20entirely%20new%20communities%2C%20with%20schools%2C%20libraries%2C%20daycares%2C%20public%20space%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20units%20of%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%2090-acre%20planned%20development%2C%20called%20Jericho%20Lands%2C%20will%20house%20up%20to%2018%2C000%20people%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0more%20than%20doubling%20the%20area's%20current%20population.%20The%20project%20is%20moving%20along%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20Vancouver%20City%20Council%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fbritish-columbia%2Fjericho-lands-policy-statement-1.7094161%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunanimously%20approved%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20policy%20statement%20in%20January%2C%20greenlighting%20the%20creation%20of%20more%20finalized%20plans.%20The%20other%20development%2C%20Heather%20Street%20Lands%2C%20a%2021-acre%20site%20in%20central%20Vancouver%2C%20will%20have%20about%202%2C600%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nations%20want%20the%20developments%20to%20be%20an%20investment%20that%20reaps%20returns%20over%20time%2C%20so%20it%20will%20offer%2099-year%20leases%20to%20homeowners%2C%20rather%20than%20selling%20off%20any%20of%20its%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%20to%20create%20a%20legacy%20economic%20engine%20for%20the%20Nations%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20community%20members%2C%20whether%20that%20be%20the%20preservation%20and%20retention%20of%20culture%2C%20art%2C%20language%2C%20healthcare%2C%20any%20other%20kind%20of%20employment%20training%20procurement%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElisa%20Campbell%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20at%20the%20Canada%20Lands%20Company%2C%20the%20arm%20of%20the%20federal%20government%20partnering%20with%20the%20three%20First%20Nations%2C%20called%20the%20Jericho%20and%20Heather%20Street%20Lands%20projects%20%26quot%3Btransformational%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bglobally%20exceptional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20just%20properties%2C%20these%20are%20communities%20that%20are%20in%20the%20broader%20context%20of%20a%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Campbell%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20city-building%20moments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20pre-construction%20approval%20process%20has%20been%20slow%20because%20the%20land%20isn't%20First%20Nations%20reserve%20land%2C%20and%20is%20subject%20to%20all%20of%20the%20government's%20land-use%20regulations.%20Heather%20Lands%20has%20been%20underway%20for%20a%20decade%20already%20and%20the%20project%20still%20isn't%20done%20with%20the%20municipal%20approvals%20process.%20Jericho%20Lands%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20between%2020%20and%2030%20years%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20housing%20projects%20aren't%20the%20only%20major%20developments%20underway%20on%20indigenous%20land%20in%20Canada.%20Just%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Vancouver%2C%20the%20Malahat%20First%20Nation%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdailyhive.com%2Fvancouver%2Fmalahat-first-nation-vancouver-island-battery-manufacturing-facility%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20a%20100%2C000-square-foot%20battery%20plant%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20company%20Energy%20Plug%20Technologies%20on%20the%20Nation's%20land.%20The%20factory%20will%20create%20in-demand%20lithium-iron-phosphate%20battery%20storage%20and%20create%20about%20100%20new%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENIMBY%20pushback%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20housing%20developments%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fbritish-columbia%2Fkits-point-judicial-review-vancouver-squamish-nation-senakw-1.6608352%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efaced%20pushback%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20some%20community%20members.%20Sen%CC%93%C3%A1%E1%B8%B5w%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvancouversun.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Fb-c-court-rejects-challenge-to-huge-squamish-nation-housing-project-in-vancouver%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvived%20a%20legal%20challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20fall%20when%20a%20British%20Columbia%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20rejected%20a%20claim%20that%20the%20local%20community%20wasn't%20sufficiently%20engaged%20in%20the%20planning%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20development's%20critics%20have%20attempted%20to%20weaponize%20Native%20American%20philosophy%20against%20it.%20In%20one%20case%2C%20former%20Vancouver%20city%20councilor%20Gordon%20Price%20argued%20that%20the%20First%20Nations%20cannot%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bland%20defenders%26quot%3B%20when%20they're%20building%20concrete%20high%20rises.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20big%20gap%20between%20that%20and%20an%20indigenous%20way%20of%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20Price%2C%20who%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20First%20Nations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-8mf-t2tqSw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CBC%20Vancouver%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupporters%20reject%20Price's%20argument%2C%20noting%20that%20building%20housing%20and%20sustainable%20communities%20are%20both%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20the%20First%20Nations%20and%20the%20broader%20city.%20Bates%20College%20environmental%20studies%20professor%20Tyler%20Harper%20has%20called%20this%20tendency%20for%20non-indigenous%20Canadians%20and%20Americans%20to%20stereotype%20indigenous%20communities%20as%20conservationists%20%26quot%3Bsentimental%20racism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndigenous%20people%20are%20reduced%20to%20vehicles%20for%20timeless%2C%20pre-historical%20knowledge%20%E2%80%93%20wish%20fulfillment%20for%20white%20progressives%20dreaming%20of%20a%20prelapsarian%20age%20before%20capital%20and%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTyler_A_Harper%2Fstatus%2F1759636229052625197%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanadians%20aren't%20used%20to%20seeing%20Indigenous%20people%20occupy%20places%20that%20are%20socially%2C%20economically%20or%20geographically%20valuable%2C%20like%20Sen%CC%93%C3%A1%E1%B8%B5w%2C%26quot%3B%20indigenous%20writer%20Michelle%20Cyca%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmacleans.ca%2Fsociety%2Fsen%25cc%2593a%25e1%25b8%25b5w-vancouver%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20recently%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20MacLean's.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20remarkable%20because%20it's%20a%20restoration%20of%20our%20authority%20and%20presence%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20Canadian%20city.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22544%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20residential%20towers%20and%20a%20courtyard%20in%20the%20Sen%CC%93a%CC%81k%CC%B1w%20development%20in%20Vancouver.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601f6841caec1275a694e2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22817%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20residential%20towers%20and%20a%20courtyard%20in%20the%20Sen%CC%93a%CC%81k%CC%B1w%20development%20in%20Vancouver.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Squamish%20Nation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20this%20kind%20of%20development%20happen%20in%20the%20US%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20housing%20or%20infrastructure%20developments%20on%20US%20tribal%20land%20that%20match%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20First%20Nations%20projects%20in%20Canada.%20While%20some%20Native%20American%20tribes%20have%20spearheaded%20significant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftucson.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fbusiness%2Fpascua-yaqui-tribe-opens-first-master-planned-community-in-tucson%2Farticle_fd4f5ade-e83d-11ed-a4b2-e301f69dc840.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Pascua%2520Yaqui%2520Tribe%2520has%2520finished%2520its%2520first%2520master%2520planned%2CThe%2520Homes%2520at%2520Yaqui%2520Square%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehousing%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20indigenous-owned%20land%20in%20the%20US%20isn't%20in%20the%20most%20valuable%20housing%20markets.%20Other%20economic%20development%20efforts%20in%20the%20US%20have%20been%20largely%20focused%20on%20the%20gaming%20industry%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fdigest%2Ffeb03%2Fsocial-and-economic-impact-native-american-casinos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecasinos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20picture%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20legacy%20of%20Indian%20removal%20is%20that%20it%20forced%20so%20many%20tribes%20onto%20marginal%20land%20that%20they%20are%20excluded%20from%20some%20of%20the%20highest%20value%20areas%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Armlovich%2C%20a%20senior%20housing-policy%20analyst%20at%20the%20Niskanen%20Center%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPro-housing%20and%20development%20advocates%20like%20Armlovich%20are%20%26quot%3Bopen-mouthed%20in%20awe%20of%20just%20what%20an%20incredible%20thing%20they're%20working%20on%20in%20Vancouver%2C%26quot%3B%20Armlovich%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPro-housing%20advocates%20say%20economic%20development%20projects%20on%20Indian%20land%20are%20possible%20if%20local%20and%20state%20governments%20take%20action%20to%20restore%20ancestral%20land%20in%20cities%20to%20tribes%20that%20are%20interested%20in%20development%2C%20or%20otherwise%20wor