Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20131%20climate%20events%20in%20the%20US%20between%202010%20and%202020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-climate-change-crisis-extreme-weather-is-costing-you-2023-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTwo%2520trillion%252C%2520six%252Dhundred%2520and%2Ctopped%2520%25241%2520billion%2520in%2520damage.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20exceeded%20%241%20billion%20in%20damages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%2051%25%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%20decade.%20Longero%20said%20because%20of%20these%20growing%20climate%20risks%2C%20she%20expects%20rates%20to%20stay%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20costs%20as%20low%20as%20possible%2C%20Longero%20recommends%20drivers%20travel%20safely%20and%20do%20their%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrioritize%20safety%20when%20behind%20the%20wheel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20safe%20driving%20important%20to%20avoid%20collisions%2C%20it%20also%20saves%20drivers%20money.%20According%20to%20personal%20finance%20company%20NerdWallet%2C%20full%20coverage%20car%20insurance%20premiums%20nearly%20double%20if%20a%20driver%20is%20at%20fault%20for%20a%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETickets%20for%20speeding%2C%20texting%20while%20driving%2C%20or%20driving%20under%20the%20influence%20are%20likely%20to%20raise%20a%20driver's%20insurance%20premiums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELongero%20said%20she%20often%20uses%20an%20app%20that%20tracks%20her%20harsh%20braking%2C%20how%20many%20times%20she%20checks%20her%20phone%2C%20and%20other%20data%20to%20demonstrate%20safe%20driving%20behavior%20to%20her%20insurer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20type%20of%20vehicle%20a%20person%20drives%20also%20determines%20their%20insurance%20prices.%20Longero%20said%20insurance%20rates%20are%20generally%20lower%20for%20bigger%20vehicles%2C%20cars%20with%20lots%20of%20safety%20features%2C%20and%20car%20brands%20that%20have%20high%20safety%20ratings.%20Family-friendly%20cars%20typically%20cost%20less%20to%20insure%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2