d%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20true%3A%20Almost%20everyone%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20lying%20about%20it%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20know%20investors%20have%20an%20appetite%20for%20all%20things%20artificial%20intelligence%20right%20now%2C%20and%20they're%20eager%20to%20show%20off%20how%20they're%20integrating%20the%20new%20tech%20into%20their%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20say%20they%20are.%20The%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission's%20chair%2C%20Gary%20Gensler%2C%20recently%20warned%20about%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fartificial-intelligence-investment-ai-washing-sec-gary-gensler-tech-stocks-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20washing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20companies%20giving%20off%20a%20false%20impression%20that%20they're%20using%20AI%20so%20they%20can%20amp%20up%20investors.%20And%20while%20some%20companies%20are%20simply%20exaggerating%20the%20tech%20they%20do%20legitimately%20use%2C%20others%20have%20taken%20it%20a%20step%20further.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20SEC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2F2024-36%3Fcampaign_id%3D4%26emc%3Dedit_dk_20240319%26instance_id%3D117968%26nl%3Ddealbook%26regi_id%3D227909179%26segment_id%3D161182%26te%3D1%26user_id%3D4657938b1c743f13e5872e4433833899%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettled%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20a%20pair%20of%20investment%20advisors%20that%20were%20accused%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20misleading%20statements%26quot%3B%20about%20how%20they're%20using%20AI.%20The%20regulator%20said%20one%20of%20the%20firms%2C%20Delphia%2C%20claimed%20it%20used%20AI%20to%20%26quot%3Bpredict%20which%20companies%20and%20trends%20are%20about%20to%20make%20it%20big%20and%20invest%20in%20them%20before%20everyone%20else%26quot%3B%20when%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20didn't.%20The%20other%2C%20Global%20Predictions%2C%20falsely%20called%20itself%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20regulated%20AI%20financial%20advisor%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20SEC.%20The%20firms%20agreed%20to%20pay%20a%20combined%20%24400%2C000%20in%20civil%20penalties%20without%20admitting%20or%20denying%20the%20SEC's%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20companies%20aren't%20being%20accused%20of%20breaking%20the%20law%20with%20their%20AI%20chatter%2C%20but%20they're%20definitely%20posturing%20around%20it.%20An%20analysis%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fai-stocks-sp500-4q-tech-earnings-artificial-intelligence-goldman-sachs-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E36%25%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies%20mentioned%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20calls%2C%20a%20record%20high.%20Businesses%20were%20just%20showing%20up%20at%20Nvidia's%20little%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-humanoid-robots-jensen-huang-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Woodstock%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20%E2%80%94%20a%20four-day%20AI%20conference%20held%20in%20an%20arena%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Ffor-these-companies-it-feels-good-to-be-in-nvidias-orbit-36dd03fe%3Fmod%3Dbusiness_lead_pos3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehoping%20to%20get%20some%3C%2Fa%3E%20hiring%20halo%20effect%20from%20merely%20being%20in%20the%20chipmaker's%20presence.%20As%20to%20how%20much%20%3Cem%3Ethere%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20there%20on%20many%20of%20these%20AI%20claims%2C%20well%2C%20there's%20some%20hyperbole%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20certain%20grandiosity%20to%20what%20is%20being%20discussed%20in%20terms%20of%20potential%2C%20and%20I%20think%20part%20of%20it%20is%20people%20don't%20know%20if%20or%20when%20some%20of%20these%20things%20are%20going%20to%20be%20achievable%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Kessler%2C%20the%20global%20sector%20lead%20of%20technology%2C%20media%2C%20and%20telecommunications%20at%20Third%20Bridge%20Group%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20very%20excited%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20but%20these%20things%20aren't%20going%20to%20happen%20overnight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20companies%20are%20clearly%20just%20bolting%20on%20AI%20ideas%20to%20their%20existing%20businesses%2C%20even%20projects%20that%20are%20explicitly%20about%20developing%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20this%20tech%20are%20hitting%20stumbling%20blocks.%20Google's%20Gemini%20rollout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-woke-images-ai-chatbot-criticism-controversy-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20a%20mess%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20criticism%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20and%20biased%20and%20seemingly%20can't%20decide%20whether%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20better%20or%20worse%20than%20Adolf%20Hitler.%20And%20while%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20generated%20a%20lot%20of%20buzz%20last%20year%2C%20it's%20still%20got%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbot-chatgpt-google-microsofty-lying-search-belief-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etendency%20to%20make%20stuff%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20release%20of%20ChatGPT%20was%20a%20brilliant%20marketing%20campaign%20in%20some%20sense.%20It%20really%20worked%20very%20well.%20It%20completely%20mesmerized%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Daron%20Acemoglu%2C%20an%20institute%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20MIT%20and%20a%20coauthor%20of%20the%20recently%20released%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2dfc4c58947dd7a402d49d4d37050661c6115d0ca580aabce2eea732c9d646e6%26postID%3D66018564a5d8cce50deac9e5%26postSlug%3Dgenerative-ai-exaggeration-openai-nvidia-microsoft-chatgpt-jobs-investors-markets-2024-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPower-Progress-Thousand-Year-Technology-Prosperity%252Fdp%252F1541702530%253Fots%253D1%2526tag%253Dcurbedcom06-20%2526linkCode%253Dw50%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPower%20and%20Progress%3A%20Our%201000-Year%20Struggle%20Over%20Technology%20%26amp%3B%20Prosperity%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20there%20were%20some%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20impressive%20achievements%26quot%3B%20embedded%20in%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20could%20be%20indicative%20of%20what's%20possible%2C%20but%20OpenAI%20hyped%20up%20the%20product%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20to%20raise%20money%2C%20attract%20talent%2C%20and%20compete%20in%20the%20hypercompetitive%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-chatgpt-openai-ceo-career-net-worth-ycombinator-prepper-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%20and%20the%20poster%20child%2Fmessiah%20for%20the%20AI%20industry%20still%20speaks%20about%20the%20tech%20in%20a%20nebulous%2C%20nonspecific%2C%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20overstated%20manner.%20As%20the%20tech%20writer%20Ed%20Zitron%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wheresyoured.at%2Fpeakai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he's%20said%20his%20kids%20have%20more%20AI%20friends%20than%20human%20friends%20and%20that%20the%20tech%20will%20replace%20almost%20everything%20marketing%20agencies%20do%2C%20among%20other%20eyebrow-raising%20claims.%20It's%20not%20the%20case%20that%20Altman's%20being%20disingenuous%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20just%20that%20it's%20not%20super%20clear%20what%20the%20present%20capabilities%20of%20the%20technology%20even%20truly%20are%2C%20let%20alone%20what%20they%20might%20be%20in%20the%20future%2C%20so%20making%20bold%2C%20concrete%20claims%20about%20the%20way%20it's%20going%20to%20affect%20society%20seems%20presumptuous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20clear%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20there's%20a%20belief%20that%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20be%20made%2C%20and%20overselling%20has%20become%20a%20near-constant%20of%20the%20AI%20landscape.%20While%20the%20semiconductor%20industry%20is%20seeing%20an%20enormous%20amount%20of%20demand%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20side%20of%20AI%2C%20not%20all%20companies%20in%20the%20arena%20are%20created%20equal.%20Companies%20such%20as%20Nvidia%2C%20AMD%2C%20and%20Broadcom%20are%20big%20winners%2C%20but%20then%20there%20are%20others%20out%20there%20%26quot%3Bwho%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Angelo%20Zino%2C%20a%20senior%20industry%20analyst%20at%20CFRA%20Research%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20they%20would%20kind%20of%20spin%20it%20is%20somewhere%20along%20the%20lines%20of%2C%20'We%20expect%20AI%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20beneficiary%20of%20our%20business%2C%20and%20we%20see%20increasing%20orders%20related%20to%20AI%2C'%20and%20it%20might%20be%20some%20hard-disk-drive%20maker%2C%20which%20isn't%20necessarily%20an%20AI%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20that%20are%20really%20moving%20and%20shaking%20in%20AI%20are%20on%20shifty%20ground%20at%20times.%20Tech%20giants%20such%20as%20Google%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dfc81e81f778bae222d8660c6eb6b42ca4416745d54f09f50e8995d6864d9f317%26postID%3D66018564a5d8cce50deac9e5%26postSlug%3Dgenerative-ai-exaggeration-openai-nvidia-microsoft-chatgpt-jobs-investors-markets-2024-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fgenerative-ai-providers-quietly-tamp-down-expectations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etelling%3C%2Fa%3E%20sales%20executives%20to%20hold%20their%20horses%20on%20how%20they're%20pitching%20their%20generative-AI%20capabilities%20to%20clients%2C%20The%20Information%20reported.%20Just%20because%20you%20layer%20AI%20into%20your%20offering%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20actually%20helpful%20to%20your%20customers%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20them%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20lot%20for%20it.%20Take%20the%20example%20of%20Microsoft's%20Copilot%2C%20which%20the%20company%20isn't%20breaking%20out%20a%20ton%20of%20detail%20on%2C%20revenuewise%2C%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20these%20companies%20are%20not%20yet%20showcasing%20exactly%20what%20type%20of%20revenue%20they're%20getting%20from%20AI%20yet%20because%20it's%20still%20so%20small%2C%26quot%3B%20Zino%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20nontech%20companies%20talking%20about%20AI%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20tell%20what%20exactly%20anyone%20means%20or%20what's%20hope%20versus%20reality.%20I%20recently%20found%20myself%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20bank%20executive%20who%20touted%20her%20firm's%20efforts%20in%20generative%20AI.%20When%20I%20pressed%20to%20find%20out%20what%20she%20was%20talking%20about%2C%20thinking%20it%20was%20something%20big%2C%20she%20told%20me%20they%20were%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20representatives%20in%20call%20centers%20look%20up%20information.%20That's%20probably%20nice%20for%20newer%20employees%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20hang%20of%20things.%20However%2C%20it%20isn't%20game-changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20innovation%20is%20an%20important%20development.%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20reasons%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20isn't%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-crash-gundlach-ai-fed-economy-gross-hussman-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edot-com%20bubble%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-all-time-high-etfs-crypto-price-crash-boom-bust-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrypto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20this%20technology%20will%20have%20a%20meaningful%2C%20if%20yet%20undefined%2C%20impact.%20(Hopefully%2C%20not%20the%20one%20where%20it%20wipes%20out%20humanity.)%20But%20the%20financial%20incentives%20here%20make%20it%20easy%20and%20tempting%20to%20overstate%20things.%20For%20many%20companies%20and%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20space%2C%20their%20wildest%20AI%20dreams%20are%20dollar%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20cascade%20that%20if%20you%20are%20not%20talking%20about%20integrating%20generative%20AI%20into%20your%20workflow%20somehow%20if%20you're%20a%20medium%20to%20large%20company%2C%20you%20are%20sort%20of%20behind%20the%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Acemoglu%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20dreams%20of%20automation%20are%20never%20too%20far%20from%20the%20minds%20of%20many%20managers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20genuinely%20unclear%20what%20generative%20AI%20and%20what%20comes%20with%20it%20will%20bring%2C%20which%20is%20both%20unsettling%20and%20comforting.%20The%20hyperoptimistic%20and%20hyperpessimistic%20takes%20are%20likely%20wrong%2C%20meaning%20the%20truth%20will%20ultimately%20wind%20up%20being%20somewhere%20in%20the%20middle.%20But%20anyone%20who%20tells%20you%20they%20know%20exactly%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20AI%20and%20where%20it's%20headed%20is%20lying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-exaggeration-openai-nvidia-microsoft-chatgpt-jobs-investors-markets-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711532581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660328f33f923f7dab017f11