n%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20raided%20(ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish)%20Sisodia...%20they%20raided%20(Rajya%20Sabha%20MP)%20Sanjay%20Singh...%20they%20raided%20(former%20Health%20Minister%20Satyendar)%20Jain.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20find%20even%20one%20paise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sisodia%20and%20Mr%20Singh%20were%20both%20arrested%20last%20year%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%3B%20the%20former%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20February%20and%20the%20latter%20since%20October.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20dramatic%20circumstances%20last%20week%20after%20a%20Delhi%20court%20refused%20protection%20from%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20arrest%20triggered%20furious%20protests%20across%20the%20city.%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%2C%20have%20spoken%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20AAP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20raided%20us%20(Mr%20Kejriwal's%20home)%20also%20and%20found%20only%20Rs%2073%2C000.%20So%20where%20is%20all%20this%20money%20from%20the%20so-called%20liquor%20scam%3F%20Arvind%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20said%20he%20will%20reveal%20everything%20in%20court%20(tomorrow).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20country%20will%20bear%20witness.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20proof%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20given%20her%20a%20message%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'My%20body%20is%20in%20jail...%20but%20my%20spirit%20is%20with%20you'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20slammed%20BJP%20leaders%20over%20criticism%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20orders%20from%20jail%3B%20on%20Monday%20he%20had%20directed%20Ms%20Atishi%20to%20solve%20water%20supply%20and%20sewerage%20issues%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20and%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20ordered%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20to%20ensure%20a%20supply%20of%20free