elhi%20High%20Court%20today%20to%20challenge%20his%20arrest.%20Arguing%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20senior%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20ED's%20actions%20had%20violated%20his%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArrest%20without%20interrogation%20shows%20the%20current%20action%20is%20politically%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20told%20the%20court%2C%20emphasising%20that%20the%20ED%20had%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20to%20prove%20the%20crime%26quot%3B%20of%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-enforcement-directorate-wants-to-arrest-arvind-kejriwal-5284508%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20Did%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Arrest%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20believes%20the%20now-scrapped%20policy%20provided%20an%20impossibly%20high%20profit%20margin%20of%20nearly%20185%20per%20cent%20for%20retailers%20and%2012%20per%20cent%20for%20wholesalers.%20Of%20the%20latter%2C%20six%20per%20cent%20-%20over%20Rs%20600%20crore%20-%20was%20recovered%20as%20bribes%20and%20the%20money%20was%20allegedly%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20Goa%20and%20Punjab%20poll%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20labelled%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20a%20key%20conspirator%20in%20this%20case%2C%20but%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20party%20colleagues%20arrested%20in%20this%20matter%20-%20ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20and%20former%20Health%20Minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%20-%20have%20all%20denied%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20the%20opposition%20have%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20for%20using%20central%20agencies%2C%20like%20the%20ED%2C%20to%20target%20rivals%20and%20critics%20before%20the%20general%20election.%20The%20AAP%20has%20criticised%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20