0position%20as%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20may%20not%20have%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bfan%26quot%3B%20of%20Oprah%20then%2C%20but%20I%20recognized%20the%20unparalleled%20potential%20for%20growth%20and%20learning%20in%20such%20an%20environment.%20Years%20later%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20not%20being%20a%20fan%20also%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20securing%20the%20position.%20We%20were%20there%20to%20work%20on%20business%2C%20not%20praise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelebrities%20want%20people%20around%20them%20who%20can%20add%20value%20in%20an%20area%20of%20expertise%2C%20and%20offer%20a%20solution%20to%20their%20problem.%20If%20you%20only%20ask%20for%20a%20photo%20to%20put%20on%20Instagram%2C%20you%20become%20a%20fan%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20future%20business%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20I%20wasn't%20nervous.%20I%20was%20just%20curious.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20three%20years%20would%20look%20like%20but%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20from%20someone%20successful%20in%20business.%20I%20was%20intrigued%20to%20learn%20that%20beyond%20this%20person%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foprah-winfrey-left-ww-sent-stock-spiraling-spells-doom-diets-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOprah%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20whole%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20model%20and%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20job%20was%20career-defining%20and%20life-changing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20role%20was%20a%20gateway%20to%20understanding%20the%20intricacies%20of%20media%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20influence.%20I%20attended%20and%20worked%20at%20our%20O%20You!%20events%20nationwide.%20O%20You!%20events%20were%20designed%20to%20make%20the%20magazine%20come%20to%20life%20and%20celebrate%20our%20readers%20in%20a%20meaningful%20and%20enlightening%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20helped%20ensure%20all%20our%20VIP%20guests%20felt%20welcomed%20and%20their%20immediate%20needs%20were%20handled.%20Besides%20events%2C%