nsider.com%2Fbaltimore-sell-hundreds-vacant-homes-residents-for-just-1-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaltimore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20it's%20time%20to%20go%20to%20work%2C%20I%20first%20get%20on%20a%20plane%20and%20commute%20to%20Baltimore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20work%2015%20days%20and%20get%2015%20days%20off%20a%20month.%20I'll%20fly%20three%20or%20four%20days%20straight%20on%20a%20typical%20week%20and%20get%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20time%20off.%20On%20an%20average%20day%2C%20I'll%20pilot%20three%20to%20five%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sometimes%20feels%20like%20I'm%20living%20two%20different%20lives.%20When%20I'm%20away%20as%20a%20pilot%2C%20I'm%20by%20myself%2C%20but%20when%20I'm%20back%20home%2C%20I'm%20a%20husband%20and%20a%20dad%20to%20four%20kids.%20It's%20a%20different%20lifestyle%20that%20can%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-culture-social-individualism-loneliness-epidemic-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeel%20lonely%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20have%20friendships%20with%20coworkers%20as%20a%20pilot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-private-jet-pilot-what-job-like-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epilots%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20every%20plane.%20Until%20we're%20at%20a%20cruising%20altitude%2C%20both%20of%20the%20pilots%20in%20the%20cockpit%20are%20heavily%20engaged%20and%20focused.%20Once%20we%20get%20there%2C%20we%20often%20turn%20on%20autopilot.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20pilots%20become%20system%20monitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rarely%20know%20the%20other%20pilot%20I'm%20flying%20with.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20I'm%20meeting%20that%20person%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Before%20the%20flight%20begins%2C%20I'll%20introduce%20myself%20and%20try%20to%20get%20to%20know%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20practice%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside