e%20bomb%20that%20landed%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Petropavlivka%20on%20Feb.%2013%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Scott%20Peterson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20still%20learning%26quot%3B%20and%20coming%20up%20with%20solutions%2C%20he%20said%2C%20enabling%20Russian%20forces%20to%20advance%20despite%20some%20of%20the%20issues%20they've%20had%20with%20positional%20and%20trench%20warfare%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOperating%20over%20Ukraine%20with%20'impunity'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGlide%20bombs%20have%20flight%20control%20surfaces%20and%20are%20standoff%20weapons%2C%20meaning%20that%20attacking%20aircraft%20can%20release%20them%20at%20a%20distance%20from%20a%20target%20instead%20of%20directly%20above%20it%20(unlike%20conventional%20gravity%20bombs)%2C%20which%20helps%20reduce%20the%20aircraft's%20exposure%20to%20enemy%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShort%20flight%20times%2C%20small%20radar%20signatures%2C%20and%20non-ballistic%20trajectories%20make%20glide%20bombs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shoot-down-russian-planes-f16-glide-bombs-military-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20difficult%20to%20intercept%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well.%20And%20while%20Ukraine%20has%20warned%20throughout%20the%20war%20that%20these%20munitions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-glide-bombs-headache-ukraine-moscow-making-new-ones-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20cause%20serious%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20past%20few%20months%20have%20proven%20this%20concern%20to%20be%20especially%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussian%20forces%20have%20significantly%20increased%20guided%20and%20unguided%20glide-bomb%20strikes%20against%20rear%20and%20frontline%20Ukrainian%20positions%20in%202024%2C%20notably%20employing%20mass%20glide-bomb%20strikes%20to%20tactical%20effect%20in%20their%20seizure%20of%20Avdiivka%20in%20mid-Febr