making%20a%20big%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nirupam%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FElectionsWithNDTV%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ElectionsWithNDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Congress%20wants%20to%20save%20the%20party%2C%20it%20should%20break%20alliance%20with%20Shiv%20Sena%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%20leader%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20on%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-Sena's%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FLokSabhaElection2024%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23LokSabhaElection2024%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAXLAgEtgBk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAXLAgEtgBk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1772889539943469256%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%2C%20which%20has%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20second%20highest%20after%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(80)%2C%20will%20vote%20in%20five%20phases%20starting%20from%20April%2019.%20Results%20will%20be%20announced%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20parties%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20and%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20-%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20finalise%20a%20seat-sharing%20plan%20despite%20a%20flurry%20of%20meetings%20before%20polling%20in%20the%20state%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20Thackeray%20finally%20took%20a%20call%20and%20announced%20its%20candidates%20for%2016%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20any%20candidate%20for%20Mumbai%20South-Central%2C%20a%20seat%20which%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20as%20well%