11520093-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345840%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKanchan%20claims%20she%20is%20the%20first%20such%20farmer%20to%20practice%20turmeric%20farming%20in%20this%20region.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20turmeric%20farming%2C%20the%20soil%20is%20usually%20mounded%20around%20the%20base%20of%20a%20plant%20to%20get%20large%20rhizomes.%20At%20first%2C%20Kanchan%20says%20she%20did%20not%20know%20the%20right%20time%20to%20earth%20up%20the%20plant.%20She%20later%20learned%20that%20it%20was%20done%20a%20month%20after%20planting%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20sowing%20period%20is%20between%20June%20and%20July%2C%20the%20crop%20is%20ready%20for%20harvest%20by%20February-end.%20She%20points%20out%20that%20it%20is%20very%20important%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20used%20for%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9COur%20region%20is%20famous%20for%20black%20soil%20that%20is%20suitable%20for%20wheat%20cultivation.%20However%2C%20a%20well-drained%20sandy%20loam%20soil%20rich%20in%20humus%20content%20works%20well%20for%20growing%20turmeric%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20black%20soil%20is%20soft%20when%20wet%20but%20forms%20hard%20blocks%20when%20it%20gets%20dry.%20So%2C%20we%20need%20a%20sandy%20loamy%20solid%20that%20is%20well-drained.%20In%20our%20district%2C%20only%20a%20few%20blocks%20including%20our%20Kesla%20block%20have%20such%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%20required%20for%20boosting%20turmeric%20growth%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20use%20cow%20dung%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejeevamrut%20%3C%2Fem%3E(liquid%20organic%20manure)%20to%20boost%20the%20fertility%20of%20the%20soil.%20Besides%2C%20as%20turmeric%20in%20itself%20is%20antiseptic%20and%20herbal%2C%20there%20are%20fewer%20chances%20of%20pest%20attack.%20Even%20if%20pests%20attack%20the%20crop%2C%20we%20use%20Trichoderma%20biopesticides%20to%20control%20the%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20careful%20of%20growing%20a%20new%20crop%2C%20Kanchan%20sowed%20and%20used%20only%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20to%20sow%20eight%20quintals%20of%20turmeric%20root.%20After%20eight%20months%2C%20she%20harvested%20bumper%20produce%20of%20100%20quintals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Last%20year%2C%20Kanchan%20got%20a%20bountiful%20harvest%20of%20400%20quintals%2C%20earning%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345839%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELast%20year%2C%20Kanchan%20got%20a%20bountiful%20harvest%20of%20400%20quintals%2C%20earning%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProcessing%20raw%20turmeric%20for%20good%20returns%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20harvesting%20the%20rhizomes%2C%20Kanchan%20processes%20the%20entire%20produce%20to%20sell%20it%20in%20powdered%20form.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20wash%20the%20roots%2C%20we%20boil%20them%20in%20water%20and%20dry%20them%20completely%20under%20the%20sunlight.%20Thereafter%2C%20we%20peel%20the%20roots%20and%20grind%20them.%20It%20takes%20about%2015%20days%20to%20process%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekachhi%20haldi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(raw%20turmeric)%20into%20powder%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20batch%20of%20100%20quintals%2C%20only%2020%20quintals%20are%20left%20after%20processing.%20But%20this%20step%20is%20extremely%20advantageous%20as%20powder%20turmeric%20gets%20higher%20returns%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Kanchan%20earned%20Rs%203%20lakh%20against%20the%20input%20costs%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20Currently%2C%20she%20has%20expanded%20turmeric%20cultivation%20on%2010%20acres%20of%20land.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20season%2C%20we%20expect%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2030%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Kanchan%20makes%201%20kg%20packets%20of%20powdered%20turmeric%20and%20sells%20entire%20produce%20on%20the%20farm%20itself.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20local%20market%20as%20we%20have%20earned%20great%20demand%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20By%20the%20time%20any%20outside%20customer%20reaches%20us%2C%20we%20have%20usually%20sold%20all%20our%20produce.%20Also%2C%20we%20sell%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260973%2Frajasthan-couple-turmeric-revolution-earns-lakhs-suicides-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20turmeric%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20Rs%20150%20per%20kg%20compared%20to%20Rs%20240%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20local%20market.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20any%20issue%20lowering%20the%20price%20as%20our%20cost%20of%20production%20becomes%20less%20with%20organic%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanchan%20claims%20she%20is%20the%20first%20such%20farmer%20to%20practice%20turmeric%