2%80%94%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjansuraksha.gov.in%2FFiles%2FPMJJBY%2FENGLISH%2FRules.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Jeevan%20Jyoti%20Bima%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(PMJJBY).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20his%20account%20was%20debited%20on%2029%20December%202022%2C%20upset%20that%20the%20bank%2C%20supposed%20to%20safeguard%20his%20money%2C%20took%20it%20without%20permission%2C%20Kumar%2C%2026%2C%20sought%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20insurance%20application%20form%20from%20the%20bank%20under%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcic.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FRTI-Act_English.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERight%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%202%20February%202023%2C%20his%20bank%2C%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%2C%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CApplication%20form%20not%20found%20for%20the%20aforesaid%20insurance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20not%20granted%20him%20a%20refund%20for%20this%20unsolicited%20insurance.%20He%20told%3Cb%3E%C2%A0Article%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0in%20an%20interview%20that%20he%20was%20still%20looking%20for%20a%20way%20%E2%80%9Cto%20get%20out%20of%20this%20dirty%20system%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20him%2C%20many%20across%20the%20country%20have%20protested%20unauthorised%20debits%20from%20their%20bank%20accounts%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20insurance%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20life%20insurance%2C%20banks%20have%20also%20been%20enrolling%20customers%20without%20consent%20in%20the%20accident%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20called%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjansuraksha.gov.in%2FFiles%2FPMSBY%2FENGLISH%2FRules.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Suraksha%20Bima%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(PMSBY).%20These%20complaints%20also%20extend%20to%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20micro-pension%20scheme%2C%20called%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnpscra.nsdl.co.in%2Fnsdl%2Fscheme-details%2FOct162015.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAtal%20Pension%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(APY).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Kumar%20got%20enrolled%20in%20PMJJBY%20without%20consent%2C%20his%20mother%20was%20enrolled%20in%20the%20APY%20without%20consent%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20PMJJBY%20premium%20is%20Rs%20436%20a%20year%2C%20PMSBY%20costs%20Rs%2020%20a%20year.%20Once%20a%20customer%20is%20subscribed%20to%20these%20schemes%2C%20the%20fees%20are%20deducted%20automatically%20from%20his%2Fher%20account%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMJJBY%20provides%20a%20cover%20of%20Rs%20200%2C000%20to%20a%20policyholder%E2%80%99s%20nominee%20in%20the%20event%20of%20death%20due%20to%20any%20reason.%20The%20PMSBY%20provides%20Rs%20200%2C000%20in%20case%20of%20death%20due%20to%20an%20accident%20and%20Rs%20100%2C000%20in%20case%20of%20a%20severe%20accident%20injury.%20The%20APY%20offers%20a%20monthly%20pension%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20after%20the%20age%20of%2060.%20The%20monthly%20fee%20depends%20on%20the%20pension%20plan%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20those%20enrolled%20in%20insurance%20schemes%20without%20consent%20are%20not%20aware%20that%20they%20are%20paying%20a%20premium%20for%20an%20insurance%20cover.%20This%20prevents%20family%20members%20from%20availing%20the%20schemes%E2%80%99%20benefits%2C%20rendering%20their%20premium%20payments%E2%80%94unauthorised%20to%20begin%20with%E2%80%94futile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolicy%20certificates%20of%20such%20customers%2C%20accessed%20by%20this%20reporter%2C%20showed%20bogus%20nominees.%20This%20also%20restricts%20policyholders%E2%80%99%20families%20from%20availing%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20these%20low-cost%20welfare%20schemes%20in%20May%202015%20to%20provide%20financial%20security%20to%20the%20poor.%20From%20the%20beginning%2C%C2%A0%20banks%20faced%20allegations%20of%20enrolling%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes%20through%20fraudulent%20practices%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsushilmaheshwar%2Fstatus%2F606999850983366657%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.complaintboard.in%2Fcomplaints-reviews%2Ficici-l414630.html%23c1795625%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fsbi-kerala-making-customers-join-pms-suraksha-bima-yojana-without-permission-30317%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20purportedly%20because%20of%20government%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20previous%20reports%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fhow-an-aadhaar-fraud-forces-the-poor-into-paying-for-welfare-schemes-they-do-not-want-63f57eb9e8d15%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fbanks-have-been-charging-customers-for-government-insurance-they-never-wanted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20reporter%20has%20described%20various%20ploys%20through%20which%20banks%E2%80%99%20branches%20and%20field%20staff%20force%20these%20schemes%20upon%20their%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20evidence%20reveals%20that%20this%20malpractice%20has%20since%20been%20institutionalised%2C%20with%20regional%2C%20zonal%20and%20even%20head%20offices%20executing%20these%20frauds%20and%20forcing%20branches%20to%20conceal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHuge%20Targets%2C%20Quick%20Fixes%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quickest%20albeit%20illegal%20way%20to%20enrol%20a%20high%20number%20of%20customers%20appears%20to%20be%20what%20is%20called%20%E2%80%9Cbulk%20activation%E2%80%9D%2C%20where%20banks%20can%20upload%20and%20approve%20many%20customers%E2%80%99%20details%20into%20the%20insurance-activation%20portal%20all%20at%20once%20using%20a%20spreadsheet%20or%20another%20bulk%20upload%20file.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20steep%20the%20targets%2C%20they%20can%20be%20met%20with%20just%20a%20few%20clicks%20as%20long%20as%20the%20bank%20does%20not%20mind%20enrolling%20customers%20without%20their%20knowledge.%20Bank%20employees%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falashshukla%2Fstatus%2F1744036406429733166%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposts%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20X%20illustrate%20that%20this%20mode%20of%20enrolling%20customers%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%20at%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20an%20officers%E2%80%99%20union%20of%20government-run%20UCO%20Bank%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20its%20managing%20director%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20alleging%20that%20account%20holders%20in%20Dehradun%20were%20illegally%20enrolled%20in%20these%20government%20schemes%20from%20the%20back-end%20by%20the%20head%20office.%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20that%20in%20July-end%2C%20the%20zonal%20office%20in%20Dehradun%20sent%20the%20branches%20a%20list%20of%20accounts%20eligible%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20and%20asked%20the%20branches%20to%20activate%20the%20schemes%20in%20all%20of%20them%2C%20the%20letter%20said.%20Many%20branch%20managers%20refused%20to%20do%20so%20without%20customers%E2%80%99%20consent%2C%20only%20for%20the%20head%20office%20to%20do%20this%20from%20the%20back-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%E2%80%99s%20letter%20said%20customer%20complaints%20began%20to%20trickle%20in%2C%20and%20branch%20managers%20requested%20their%20zonal%20office%20to%20issue%20refunds%2C%20but%20the%20zonal%20office%20instead%20instructed%20them%20to%20collect%20and%20backdate%20enrolment%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20of%20government-owned%20Canara%20Bank%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20a%20similar%20story%20unfolded%20in%20Rajasthan%20last%20June.%20He%20said%20that%20regional%20offices%20sent%20branches%20lists%20of%20their%20customers%20eligible%20for%20PMJJBY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20employee%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20content%20management%20system%2C%20showing%20that%20PMJJBY%20was%20activated%20on%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20in%20bulk%20by%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%20posted%20in%20a%20regional%20office.%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20sent%20queries%20by%20email%20to%20this%20officer%20and%20is%20awaiting%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reporter%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fbanks-have-been-charging-customers-for-government-insurance-they-never-wanted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20illegal%20enrolment%20of%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes%20was%20based%20on%20similar%20evidence%20of%20bulk%20activation%20in%20Canara%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20West%20Bengal%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20SBI%20employee%20from%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20circle%20shared%20with%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0screenshots%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20de%20facto%20official%20WhatsApp%20group%20in%20October%202023.%20(Banks%20do%20not%20recognise%20WhatsApp%20as%20an%20official%20mode%20of%20communication%2C%20but%20liaisoning%20between%20regional%2Fzonal%20offices%20and%20branches%20does%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthekanal.in%2Fen-IN%2Fdetails%2F65437f7df146df001331d97c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20WhatsApp%20groups.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WhatsApp%20screenshots%20sent%20by%20the%20SBI%20employee%20showed%20bank%20employees%20being%20given%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20initiate%20bulk%20enrolment%20of%20customers%20in%20PMSBY.%20This%20employee%20also%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20the%20bulk%20upload%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Gujarat%20resident%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20SBI%20account%20was%20auto-debited%20for%20PMJJBY%20on%2019%20January%202024.%20He%20said%20that%20when%20she%20went%20to%20her%20branch%20to%20seek%20an%20explanation%2C%20the%20branch%20told%20her%20that%20many%20accounts%20were%20debited%20because%20of%20a%20technical%20error%2C%20and%20now%20the%20bank%20was%20offering%20a%20full%20refund.%20To%20refund%20the%20money%2C%20the%20bank%20asked%20her%20to%20fill%20a%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162036%2FUntitled.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22762%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162036%2FUntitled.jpeg%20762w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162036%2FUntitled-300x256.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703267%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAt%20this%20SBI%20branch%2C%20customers%20who%20questioned%20unauthorised%20debits%20for%20insurance%20were%20readily%20handed%20a%20refund%20form.%20Photo%20courtesy%20Article%2014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20customer%E2%80%99s%20husband%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20he%20spoke%20with%20the%20branch%20manager%2C%20who%20apologetically%20s