tional%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20he%20did%20not%20explicitly%20reaffirm%20India%E2%80%99s%20stance%20regarding%20China%E2%80%99s%20obligation%20to%20comply%20with%20the%202016%20arbitral%20tribunal%20ruling%20that%20invalidated%20Chinese%20claims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%20is%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20travelling%20to%20Manila%20after%20a%20stop%20at%20Singapore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20met%20with%20Filipino%20foreign%20minister%20Enrique%20A.%20Manalo%20and%20called%20on%20President%20Ferdinand%20Marcos%20Junior.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20press%20appearance%20in%20Manila%20with%20his%20counterpart%2C%20Jaishankar%20stated%20that%20prosperity%20in%20the%20region%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20served%20by%20staunch%20adherence%20to%20a%20rules-based%20order%E2%80%9D%2C%20highlighting%20the%201982%20UN%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%20(UNCLOS)%20as%20a%20foundational%20aspect%20of%20this%20approach.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20parties%20must%20adhere%20to%20it%20%5Bthe%20UNCLOS%5D%20in%20its%20entirety%2C%20both%20in%20letter%20and%20in%20spirit.%20I%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20firmly%20reiterate%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20to%20the%20Philippines%20for%20upholding%20its%20national%20sovereignty%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F37745%2FRemarks%2Bby%2BEAM%2BDr%2BS%2BJaishankar%2Bat%2Bthe%2BJoint%2BPress%2Bconference%2Bwith%2BForeign%2BMinister%2Bof%2BPhilippines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%E2%80%99s%20statement%20came%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20latest%20escalation%20in%20tensions%20between%20China%20and%20the%20Philippines%20after%20two%20Chinese%20coast%20guard%20ships%20hit%20a%20supply%20boat%20of%20the%20Filipino%20navy%20with%20water%20cannons%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20a%20series%20of%20confrontations%20between%20the%20countries%20in%20the%20high%20seas%2C%20with%20China%20attempting%20to%20dislodge%20Philippines%20forces%20from%20the%20disputed%20Second%20Thomas%20Shoal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20summoning%20the%20charge%20d%E2%80%99affaires%20of%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%2C%20the%20Philippines%20had%20lodged%20its%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdfa.gov.ph%2Fdfa-news%2Fdfa-releasesupdate%2F34388-statement-released-by-the-dfa-spokesperson-2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estrongest%20protest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20Chinese%20coast%20guard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20China%20responded%20that%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsouth-china-sea-philippines-shoal-f789f10b3a47ee0d22e8dec59df57eb2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20at%20a%20crossroads%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20backing%20of%20Filipino%20sovereignty%20during%20this%20period%20is%20significant%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cevolved%E2%80%9D%20stance%20on%20the%202016%20award%20is%20also%20noteworthy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202016%2C%20an%20arbitration%20tribunal%20set%20up%20under%20the%20UNCLOS%20had%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Philippines%20government%2C%20which%20had%20petitioned%20against%20China%E2%80%99s%20aggressive%20actions%20in%20the%20disputed%20oil-rich%20waters%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20arbitration%20process%2C%20has%20consistently%20argued%20that%20the%202016%20ruling%20by%20the%20Arbitral%20Tribunal%20is%20illegal%20and%20has%20refused%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInitially%2C%20India%20had%20merely%20%E2%80%9Cnoted%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20maintaining%20a%20neutral%20position.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffor-the-first-time-india-calls-for-abiding-by-the-2016-arbitral-award-on-south-china-sea%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20June%202023%2C%20India%20shifted%20its%20position%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20advocated%20for%20compliance%20with%20the%202016%20Arbitral%20award%2C%20as%20stated%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20with%20the%20Philippines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20renewed%20tensions%20in%20the%20region%20in%20August%202023%2C%20India%20reiterated%20its%20call%20for%20adherence%20to%20international%20law.%20However%2C%20the%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20spokesperson%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-tensions-over-south-china-sea-india-tells-china-philippines-to-adhere-to-global-law%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edid%20not%20make%20any%20reference%20to%20the%202016%20ruling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Jaishankar%20did%20not%20bring%20up%20the%20alleged%20change%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20regarding%20the%20international%20arbitration%20order%20established%20under%20the%20UNCLOS%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20Manila.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20discussions%20between%20the%20foreign%20ministers%2C%20the%20attacks%20by%20the%20Houthis%20on%20vessels%20in%20Red%20Seas%20were%20also%20discussed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20noting%20both%20of%20our%20countries%E2%80%99%20significant%20contributions%20in%20merchant%20shipping%2C%20we%20explored%20possible%20cooperation%