ed%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu%2C%20a%20three-time%20MP%2C%20also%20comes%20from%20a%20prominent%20Congress%20family.%20His%20grandfather%2C%20Beant%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20CM%20of%20Punjab%20between%201992%20and%201995%2C%20was%20assassinated%20during%20the%20Khalistan%20militancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20brother%20Gurkirat%20Singh%20Kotli%20is%20still%20a%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20Khanna%2C%20a%20constituency%20in%20Ludhiana%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu%E2%80%99s%20joining%20the%20BJP%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20for%20many%20as%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20to%20suggest%20that%20he%20might%20leave%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20being%20considered%20for%20re-nomination%20from%20Ludhiana%20for%20the%20third%20time%20in%20a%20row%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Congress%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20his%20joining%20the%20BJP%20is%20tactical.%20Political%20analyst%20Harjeshwar%20Singh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20his%20style%20of%20politics%20has%20often%20remained%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20plank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20says%2C%20there%20is%20a%20large%20Hindu%20and%20migrant%20population%20in%20his%20Ludhiana%20constituency%2C%20which%20he%20has%20won%20twice%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20might%20have%20thought%20that%20winning%20the%20seat%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20may%20be%20challenging%20this%20time.%20Therefore%2C%20he%20has%20played%20a%20gamble%20by%20fighting%20as%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20and%20using%20issues%20like%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20and%20the%20Modi%20factor%20to%20sway%20his%20constituency%E2%80%99s%20voters%2C%20Harjeshwar%20Singh%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20reacting%20to%20Bittu%E2%80%99s%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20Punjab%20Congress%20president%20Amrinder%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%20told%20the%20media%20that%20it%20is%20no%20big%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20will%20not%20damage%20the%20party%20and%20that%20such%20deserters%20always%20create%20opportunities%20for%20fresh%20faces%20to%20contest%20and%20carry%20the%20party%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20Bittu%20has%20lost%20far%20more%20significance%20by%20leaving%20the%20party%20his%20family%20served%20with%20their%20blood.%20The%20Congress%20in%20Punjab%20will%20always%20be%20known%20by%20the%20supreme%20sacrifice%20of%20his%20grandfather%2C%20Beant%20Singh.%20He%20%5BBeant%20Singh%5D%20always%20wore%20a%20white%20turban%20and%20was%20a%20strong%20pillar%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20Bittu%20will%20just%20be%20another%20MP%20or%20minister%20if%20he%20wins.%20He%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20claim%20his%20identity%20as%20Sardar%20Beant%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20grandson%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Warring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Bittu%E2%80%99s%20entire%20family%20is%20still%20devoted%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20that%20his%20brother%20is%20very%20much%20with%20the%20party%20as%20a%20committed%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20Bittu%20said%20during%20his%20media%20briefing%20in%20Delhi%20that%20he%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20great%20work%20and%20dedication%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20both%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%20always%20took%20it%20positively%20whenever%20he%20raised%20the%20issues%20of%20Punjab%2C%20and%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20take%20Punjab%20forward%20but%20no%20other%20than%20the%20BJP%20has%20the%20vision%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%20so%20that%20Punjab%20is%20also%20benefited%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20by%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20development%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20Punjab%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20he%20said%20a%20record%