0taken%20to%20protect%20Chinese%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fis-chinas-investment-in-pakistan-slowing-down%2Fa-67065190%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20invested%20heavily%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20infrastructure%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20as%20part%20of%20the%20China%20Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20projects%20have%20led%20to%20a%20level%20of%20resentment%20in%20some%20local%20quarters%2C%20with%20separatist%20groups%20claiming%20those%20from%20the%20region%20benefit%20little%2C%20with%20most%20jobs%20going%20to%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20group%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%C2%A0attack%2C%20but%20Islamist%20militants%20linked%20to%20the%20Pakistani%20Taliban%2C%20known%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistani-taliban-move-into-new-territories%2Fa-65503987%5C%22%3Ethe%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20previously%20targeted%20Chinese%20interests%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-5-chinese-workers-killed-in-bombing%2Fa-68668800%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3EDW%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711460326000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24215513%2F6483091829_b0a9599ab5_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Ffive-chinese-nationals-among-six-killed-in-pakistan-suicide-bombing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20group%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%C2%A0attack%2C%20but%20Islamist%20militants%20linked%20to%20the%20Pakistani%20Taliban%2C%20known%20as%C2%A0the%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%2C%20have%20previously%20targeted%20Chinese%20interests%20in%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2