0the%20release%20of%20Bandi%20Sikhs%20are%20seen%20as%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20coalition%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20became%20amply%20clear%20after%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Punjab%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20March%2026%20that%20his%20party%20will%20fight%20all%2013%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20top%20brass%20of%20BJP%20was%20confident%20of%20bringing%20Akalis%20%E2%80%94%20which%20once%20was%20its%20trusted%20ally%20%E2%80%94%20back%20in%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20fold%2C%20the%20announcement%20hardly%20came%20as%20a%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98We%20do%20not%20engage%20in%20politics%20solely%20for%20votes.%20Parties%20from%20Delhi%20play%20vote%20politics%2C%20but%20for%20us%2C%20Punjab%20comes%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20SAD%20president%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Badal%20said%20on%20the%20recent%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Pramod%20Kumar%2C%20who%20also%20heads%20Chandigarh-based%20Institute%20for%20Development%20and%20Communication%2C%20told%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20that%20SAD%20wanted%20conditional%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20with%20assurance%20to%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20MSP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20core%20issue%20of%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20peasant%20currently%20protesting%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20it%20also%20wanted%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20in%20the%20release%20of%20Bandi%20Sikhs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20issue%20among%20section%20of%20Sikhs%20in%20Punjab%20%E2%80%94%20who%20had%20completed%20their%20jail%20term%20(Bandi%20Sikhs%20is%20a%20term%20used%20for%20Sikh%20prisoners%20languishing%20in%20various%20jails%20in%20India%20for%20their%20involvement%20during%20militancy%20in%20Punjab)%2C%20said%20Pramod.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20him%2C%20the%20BJP%20rather%20wanted%20seat%20adjustments%20for%20the%20coming%20election.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20alliance%20did%20not%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20understanding%20the%20political%20implication%20of%20the%20alliance%20talk%20failure%2C%20it%20is%20vital%20to%20know%20as%20to%20why%20these%20issues%20were%20important%20to%20SAD.%20The%20answer%20is%20closely%20knitted%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20core%20politics%20in%20Punjab%2C%20which%20revolved%20majorly%20around%20Sikh%20%3Ci%3Epanth%20%3C%2Fi%3Eand%20state%E2%80%99s%20peasantry%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20factors%20like%20sacrilege%20incidents%20and%20growing%20rural%20distress%20made%20the%20SAD%20lose%20its%20core%20base%20in%202017%20assembly%20polls%20after%20running%20two%20successive%20governments%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20SAD%20faced%20another%20setback%20after%20three%20farm%20bills%20by%20its%20alliance%20partner%20BJP%20at%20the%20centre%20in%202020%20turned%20into%20historic%20protest%20by%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%20and%20other%20states.%20Even%20though%20SAD%20officially%20broke%20off%20its%20old%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%20over%20farm%20bills%2C%20the%20political%20dynamics%20changed%20in%20Punjab%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20harped%20on%20voters%E2%80%99%20disenchantment%20against%20traditional%20parties%20and%20won%20a%20historic%20mandate%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls%2C%20with%20SAD%20reducing%20to%20just%20three%20assembly%20constituencies%20and%20BJP%20limiting%20to%20just%20two%20seats.%20The%20then%20incumbent%20Congress%20was%20equally%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20while%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20formed%20their%20election%20strategies%2C%20many%20expected%20SAD%20and%20BJP%20to%20come%20together%20to%20weave%20their%20old%20rural-urban%20magic%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalks%20officially%20began%20between%20both%20the%20parties%20as%20union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20publically%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%20But%20the%20return%20of%20farm%20protests%20last%20month%20in%20February%20%E2%80%93%20this%20time%20with%20a%20fresh%20demand%20for%20MSP%20guarantee%20law%20%E2%80%93%20again%20created%20uneasiness%20in%20possible%20ties%20between%20SAD%20and%20BJP%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20recent%20core%20committee%20meeting%20on%20March%2022%2C%20SAD%20made%20its%20mandate%20clear%20by%20passing%20a%20resolution%20which%20urged%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20honour%20its%20categorical%20written%20commitment%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Bandi%20Singhs%20who%20had%20completed%20their%20terms.%20The%20regional%20party%20also%20mentioned%20that%20it%20would%20continue%20to%20champion%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%20and%20said%20that%20all%20promises%20made%20to%20them%20must%20be%20fulfilled.A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20will%20never%20deviate%20from%20its%20historic%20role%20as%20a%20champion%20of%20the%20interests%20of%20Khalsa%20Panth%2C%20all%20minorities%20as%20well%20as%20all%20Punjabis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20implications%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20SAD%20and%20BJP%20going%20solo%2C%20Punjab%20will%20witness%20four-cornered%20fight%20just%20like%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20the%20election%20may%20likely%20remain%20a%20close%20fight%20as%20all%20the%20parties%20are%20working%20on%20different%20agendas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAD%20has%20already%20spelt%20out%20its%20focus%20on%20recovering%20its%20old%20core%20base%20as%20well%20as%20targeting%20the%20AAP%20government%2C%20claiming%20that%20Bhagwant%20Mann-led%20government%20was%20a%20complete%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20is%20harping%20on%20its%20governance%20model%20including%20fulfilment%20of%20pre-election%20promises%20like%20free%20electricity%20and%20Mohalla%20clinics%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20have%20Modi%20to%20ride%20its%20election%20juggernaut%20in%20the%20state%20and%20hope%20to%20sway%20masses%20especially%20in%20urban%20areas%20on%20the%20name%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%20and%20promise%20of%20another%20stable%20government%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20SAD%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20relied%20on%20the%20anti-AAP%20agenda.%20But%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20now%20looks%20a%20bit%20in%20disarray%20ever%20since%20it%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20AAP%20at%20the%20national%20level%20to%20prevent%20the%20NDA%20from%20coming%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20told%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20that%20the%20failure%20of%20alliance%20talks%20between%20SAD%20and%20BJP%20would%20lead%20to%20crowding%20of%20electoral%20space%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20four-cornered%20contest%20will%20lead%20to%20division%20of%20votes.%20The%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20may%20hope%20to%20be%20major%20beneficiaries%20of%20this%20influx%20while%20Akalis%20hope%20to%20secure%20seats%20on%20its%20renewed%20efforts%20to%20win%20back%20its%20old%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20is%20hopeful%20that%20it%20may%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20the%20accidental%20beneficiary%20of%20this%20flux%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pramod%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711458048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26181904%2FScreenshot-2024-03-26-at-6.16.16-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fno-alliance-between-sad-and-bjp-in-punjab-as-akalis-focus-on-recovering-lost-ground-among-farmers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20regional%20party%20also%20wanted%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20in%20the%20release%20of%20Bandi%20Sikhs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20issue%