20found%20it%20tough%20to%20save%20even%20Rs%2010%20a%20month.%20Things%20were%20not%20good.%E2%80%9D%20But%20why%20should%20women%20face%20these%20problems%20when%20they%20are%20wonderfully%20skilled%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20thought%20was%20accompanied%20by%20another.%20What%20if%20the%20women%20borrowed%20from%20the%20foreign%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344962%2Fhow-to-start-a-homestay-in-india-rules-tips-from-owners-travel-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcept%20of%20homestays%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawant%20had%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20hospitality%20extended%20to%20her%20during%20her%20stay%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Bed%20and%20Breakfasts%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20UK%20while%20she%20was%20attending%20the%20%E2%80%98Edinburgh%20International%20Festival%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20event%20that%20celebrates%20the%20performing%20arts%20on%20a%20global%20scale%2C%20in%202000.%20She%20was%20amazed%20at%20how%20the%20lady%20of%20the%20house%20earned%20by%20simply%20letting%20out%20a%20bedroom%20and%20preparing%20a%20meal%20for%20her%20guests.%20If%20the%20women%20abroad%20could%20do%20this%2C%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20women%20of%20Sindhudurg%20do%20it%20too%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-6-1710768866.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20of%20Sindhudurg%20prepare%20pickles%2C%20jams%2C%20squashes%20and%20more%20under%20the%20banner%20'Hirkani'%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-6-1710768866.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-6-1710768866-300x157